ðŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is an interactive Amazon Sales Analytics Dashboard built using Microsoft Power BI.

The dashboard provides a detailed analysis of sales performance, courier status, fulfillment types, product categories, sizes, and state-wise shipment distribution.

It helps businesses monitor operational efficiency and identify sales trends using data-driven insights.

ðŸŽ¯ Key Objectives

Analyze total sales revenue

Track courier delivery performance

Monitor top-performing product categories

Compare fulfillment types (Amazon vs Merchant)

Evaluate product size distribution

Analyze state-wise shipping trends

